        "action": "Keep the hard shoulder on Smart Motorways for emergency use only",
        "additional_details": "Using the hard shoulder of a Smart Motorway as a live lane puts road users at risk.\r\nIt gives stranded motorists no safe place to stop and prevents emergency services from reaching accidents.\r\nConsider the risks presented by using a hard shoulder as a live lane against the significant risks.",
